<ab>Apeln von Seckendorff, Pfaff <expan>gena<ex>n</ex>t</expan>, amptman czu
                        Tann </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Apels, als wir ew nehst
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und bey dem
                                <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Smid, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
                        diener, empoten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Hansen
                                <expan>Heimpecke<ex>n</ex></expan>, des Paulus Stromeirs,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex>s</expan>, wegen vom
                            <expan>Vacke<ex>n</ex>hof</expan>, <add>den ir <add>in
                                        <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan></add> vencknüsz habt</add>,
                        also <expan>bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> burgers <expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> noch
                        ledig lassen wöllet. Als etc. Das wöllen etc. Und het ir
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> czu <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan> icht <expan>czu sprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                                <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> wil ew der
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>armman<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> slewnigs
                            <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffenn, wenn er des
                            <expan>erma<ex>n</ex>t</expan> wirdt. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Mar<ex>tini</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
